        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650081
          output: 'Such reverence! The aristocrats are fascinated by our offerings.
            The exotic nature of the gifts has given us the edge we required, as
            it seems we have started a new trend among the nobility. They shall not
            forget this gesture anytime soon.

            [Gained 1 Authority]

'
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650082
          output: 'Horrible news! The gifts proved to be cheap counterfeits of the
            true articles. The refined eyes of the aristocracy were quick to spot
            the deception and were left indignant. They now believe us to be charlatans!
            This is the price of trusting outlanders!

            [Lost 1 Authority]

'
